text: The Kingdom of Holland was a country that existed from 1806 to 1810. It was in Central and North Netherlands and East Frisia in Germany. It was a puppet state created by France. The king of Holland was Louis Bonaparte. ==Related pages== *Holland ==Notes== ==References== Category:Former monarchies of Europe Category:19th-century establishments in the Netherlands Category:19th- century disestablishments in the Netherlands Category:1806 establishments in Europe Category:1810s disestablishments Category:Puppet states
